description:
Hermit Wars is a custom made map & modpack for Minecraft 1.8.9 made by HermitCraft & Friends. The modpack can be found on the Curse Launcher after this series has ended.

Hermit Wars is a last man standing, action packed RPG adventure, where health regeneration is off and mining isn’t possible. To obtain loot players needs to find loot crates and seize control over important camps and kingdoms.
